body:
Adds a soy crop and substitutes for milk and meat!


Simple Soy introduces a new crop; as the name implies, it's soy;

Soybeans have a small chance of dropping from breaking short grass;

With a Water Bottle and four Soybeans, you make a Soy Milk Bottle.
With a Soy Milk Bottle and a coagulant*, you make tofu.
With Soybeans, Tofu, Bowl, Kelp, and a Brown Mushroom, you make Miso Soup.


If Serene Seasons is installed, Soy will only grow during spring and summer;



*: Current coagulants are Egg, Apple, Kelp, and Seagrass.


PS: This mod is intended to be used with other mods; "Soy Milk Bottle" is under the neoforge milk tags, and "Tofu" is under the meat tags; the only mod getting active support currently is Farmer's Delight, but more mods are planned to get support eventually;
